{"id": 2348, "genre": 1001, "title": "职场上哪些看不见的情绪成本最让你心累？", "description": "保持鸡血满满的状态有时候比干活还累，就，强颜欢笑呗。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Ikon Images）", "record_count": 4904, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180515155819FrvtBVJR9USQmNXj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 291840, "content": "毫无意义的比较", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088059}, {"id": 291841, "content": "“可不能玩手机啊” 我玩一次手机你就少活一天谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088059}, {"id": 291842, "content": "被同事背后说坏话捅刀子～", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 291843, "content": "一些怕冷的同事经常关空调 无语?", "image": null, "praise_count": 380, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395323}, {"id": 291844, "content": "和不在一个维度的同事沟通吧，完全鸡同鸭讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 173, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355972}, {"id": 292100, "content": "经常培训到半夜10点多不让回家 说是培训 其实都是废话", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373332}, {"id": 291845, "content": "一些怕热的同事经常把空调开得很大冷气开得很低", "image": null, "praise_count": 392, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43355}, {"id": 292101, "content": "劳而无果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130546}, {"id": 291847, "content": "团队协作伙伴永远无法和你保持同频\n", "image": "img/option/option/20180710114056U3Lf7izWtcgbGx1k.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136947}, {"id": 291848, "content": "还好在家工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381896}, {"id": 291849, "content": "揣摩上司的心理活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970744}, {"id": 292617, "content": "领导拉拢不住人心，各种算计。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388681}, {"id": 291850, "content": "都看不见了，还让我讨论……就是不知道源头的心累最累啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391369}, {"id": 291851, "content": "干的很不爽的时候，想走又怕找不到下家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 284, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051333}, {"id": 291852, "content": "尬聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378583}, {"id": 293644, "content": "所在部门都是大叔级别的，只有我一个刚毕业的女生，跟他们说话都有代沟，真的很累", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387786}, {"id": 291853, "content": "部门之间的掣肘", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395096}, {"id": 291854, "content": "领导的小清续", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395367}, {"id": 291856, "content": "会做表面功夫的人升职快\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 349, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319961}, {"id": 291857, "content": "同事在办公区域抽烟，提出意见还觉得为什么别人没意见就你有意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395368}, {"id": 292113, "content": "和心术不正的小人共事，每天都得在同一间办公室相处，心里说不出的恶心还得为工作合作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396694}, {"id": 291858, "content": "领导说晚上必须加班到XX点，提前走还要报备?WTF?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345489}, {"id": 291859, "content": "没有方向\n高层也没方向\n告诉我我去做\n\n不喜欢的工作最累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299123}, {"id": 291860, "content": "没有确认好的需求跟目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249418}, {"id": 291861, "content": "创业团队心不齐，合伙人都留有后路，感觉自己才是老板却赚不到钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769800}, {"id": 291864, "content": "同事情商过低", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395388}, {"id": 292120, "content": "老板和你说，你再去找xx问一下。这意味着又要浪费一个小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369202}, {"id": 291865, "content": "看到一些同事趋炎附势，溜须拍马，需要做事的时候又能拖就拖，混加班，满嘴跑火车", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391252}, {"id": 292377, "content": "执法者的潜规则，恶心死人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359550}, {"id": 291866, "content": "表面朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395393}, {"id": 291867, "content": "开会\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334651}, {"id": 291868, "content": "话事人性质的领导。情绪导向完全跟随领导的情绪变化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395403}, {"id": 292380, "content": "那种很兩張臉的同事，老板在就装开心，老板一走马上翻脸抱怨工作多，然后老板来了又能开始拍马屁的无缝连接人格.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865461}, {"id": 291869, "content": "一直开会开会开会", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 88787}, {"id": 291870, "content": "一直开会", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 88787}, {"id": 291871, "content": "无主题无结果无准备的各种临时会议 就像清朝的裹脚布。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395406}, {"id": 291872, "content": "同事关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820731}, {"id": 291873, "content": "好好工作才是最主要的，为什么还要聊那么多不相干的八卦\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234107}, {"id": 291874, "content": "我觉得这里。部分是自己的个人问题吧～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380558}, {"id": 291876, "content": "强颜欢笑 不想上班 且不能被下属发现不想上班的丧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376955}, {"id": 292132, "content": "\n关注这些有啥用，像我把钱放在余额宝每天有利息，还可以每天在首页输入7030426领取余额宝消费红包，一般都是几块钱运气爆棚的时候有28.8元可充话费，水电费，超市购物的时候用余额宝（注意，余额宝支付）消费就可以抵扣红包，每天可领一次，别赞要脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396834}, {"id": 291877, "content": "装", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 291878, "content": "自认为深思熟虑，领导一句你做事不带脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395415}, {"id": 291879, "content": "刚入职那会老同事对你的爱搭不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378474}, {"id": 291880, "content": "没能在新员工面前成功装逼，而头痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395438}, {"id": 291881, "content": "只想不做其实蛮累的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395442}, {"id": 291882, "content": "更多的时间不是花在做事，而是花在沟通上", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599749}, {"id": 291884, "content": "在一个金融行业的国企。其他都很满意，但最累的是审批以及向领导汇报", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179825}, {"id": 293676, "content": "当感觉工资收入远配不上自己的能力，从而患得患失考虑下家的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408222}, {"id": 291885, "content": "和客户沟通的时候，上主管不做主，下客户为难自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381273}]}